==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ting
<hw>Ting</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Dan. <ets>thing</ets>, <ets>ting</ets>, Norw.
<ets>ting</ets>, or Sw. <ets>ting</ets>.]</ety> <def>In Scandinavian
countries, a legislative or judicial assembly; -- used, esp. in
composition, in titles of such bodies. See <er>Legislature</er>,
<xex>Norway</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

