==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ting
<hw>Ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[An imitative word. Cf.
<er>Tink</er>.]</ety> <def>A sharp sound, as of a bell; a
tinkling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ting</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Ting
<hw>Ting</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To sound or ring, as a bell; to
tinkle.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Holland.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ting</ent>⟦br⟧
